
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Course Guidelines";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="text-center text-primary">Your Roadmap to Mastering Space Learning!</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-muted">Follow these steps, and you'll be on your way to becoming a space expert!</p>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">📚 Step 1: Enroll & Choose Your Course</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Start by selecting the category that suits your level: Primary, Secondary, or Higher Secondary. Once enrolled, you’ll gain access to all course materials.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">📖 Step 2: Complete All Course Units</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Each course is divided into multiple units. Watch the video lessons, read the provided materials, and complete any interactive activities. Progress is tracked, so make sure you complete each unit before moving on.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">✅ Step 3: Finish All Assignments</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Before attempting the final test, complete all assignments related to the course. These are designed to reinforce your understanding and prepare you for the assessment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">📝 Step 4: Take the Final Exam</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Once you’ve completed all units and assignments, you’re ready for the final exam! This is your chance to demonstrate your knowledge and earn your certification.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">💰 Step 5: Pay for Your Certificate</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">After successfully passing the exam, you can pay the required fee to receive your official course certificate. This will serve as proof of your achievement in space learning!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">🎉 Step 6: Get Certified & Celebrate!</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Congratulations! You’ve completed the course, passed the exam, and earned your certificate. Share your achievement with your friends, add it to your portfolio, and continue exploring the wonders of space!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="text-center text-white mt-5 py-3 bg-dark">
    <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2025 Space Learning. All rights reserved. Keep exploring, keep learning!</p>
</footer>

<style>
    body {
        background: url('~/images/galaxy-background.jpg') repeat;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    .card {
        border-radius: 15px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

    .card-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #007bff;
    }
</style>
